&lt;li&gt;【3】Wang F, Xiang X, Cheng J, et al. Normface:l 2 hypersphere embedding for face verification[C]//Proceedings of the 2017 ACMon Multimedia Conference. ACM, 2017: 1041-1049.&lt;/li&gt;
